Network Set_Paths ./Resources
Network Listen GameServer 5000
Network Connect HostPlayer 127.0.0.1 5000
Network Accept GameServer Player2
Network Send HostPlayer Ready
Network Send Player2 Welcome
Network Receive HostPlayer
Network Receive Player2
Network Poll
Network Has_Data HostPlayer
Network Has_Command Player2
Network Read_Command Player2
Network Run Player2
Network Download HostPlayer Assets.zip ./Resources/Downloads/Assets.zip
Network Disconnect HostPlayer
Network Disconnect Player2
Network Stop_Listening GameServer
Return
